<p>Perfectly seasoned and roasted to perfection in your oven, this pork tenderloin is buttery tender, juicy, and so delicious! With easy ingredients and simple steps, it&#8217;s the perfect family meal.</p>
<p><picture>
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1.jpg.webp 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-300x225.jpg.webp 300w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-1024x768.jpg.webp 1024w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-768x576.jpg.webp 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-720x540.jpg.webp 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-360x270.jpg.webp 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-180x135.jpg.webp 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://recipeteacher.com/best-damn-oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin/?tp_image_id=3139" src="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1.jpg" alt="Oven roasted pork tenderloin recipe" width="1200" height="900" data-pin-title="Best Damn Oven Roasted Pork Tenderloin" data-pin-description="Oven roasted pork tenderloin. Seasoned to perfection with simple ingredients and ready in under a half hour. #porktenderloin" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1.jpg 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-720x540.jpg 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-360x270.jpg 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin1-180x135.jpg 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3139"/>
</picture>
</p>
<p>Pork tenderloin is one of the finest cuts of meat. It&#8217;s very lean and tender and can be seasoned any number of wonderful ways. For this recipe we&#8217;ll use a combination of simple pantry ingredients to season the pork, before roasting it in the oven for about 30 minutes.</p>
<h2>Make Sure It&#8217;s Pork Tenderloin</h2>
<p>There&#8217;s a few cuts of pork that have similar sounding names. Be sure the packaging clearly says pork tenderloin. They are basically long and slender and weigh around ¾lb to 1 ½lbs each. It&#8217;s also quite common to find them in 2-packs. Other similar names including pork loin, pork loin filet and pork roast are NOT pork tenderloin and require different cooking steps.</p><div id="recip-3409643831" class="recip-cookbook"><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/RecipeTeachers-Best-Damn-Cookbook-Vol/dp/B0DZGZK8QD/ref=sr_1_1?crid=3GXH1D0JSMVI6&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.cp4tYMAR0labIWEtp587LrlPFpouAYYmmcmMGLhv96LhjFTWgxEelVMBBHQhG6rCuOo9W_A_n8FDBiJ7JdHyjKEutoveRc6pjyy2bXPHIlCfM2g5K0-1_qWGauQ9OEX-w5dKDsF7ElLq0ljicuJyA97O8h7ESYYo7myZNrXhUtlzS_BmTROUtzDij-xVTBIJew7FhuKAQRUeyFKCpIdSlEZfhM0AyCSrOZx5tWFW4aA.Frr6nMpZHFS3DJ6J9A3qo6X4eRBLq9hKHi5ofwmORkY&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=best+damn+cookbook&amp;qid=1743858919&amp;sprefix=best+damn+cook%2Caps%2C125&amp;sr=8-1"><picture>
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4.png.webp 2560w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-300x115.png.webp 300w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-1024x393.png.webp 1024w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-768x295.png.webp 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-1536x589.png.webp 1536w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-2048x785.png.webp 2048w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-720x276.png.webp 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-360x138.png.webp 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-180x69.png.webp 180w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-150x58.png.webp 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4.png" alt="" width="2560" height="982" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4.png 2560w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-300x115.png 300w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-1024x393.png 1024w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-768x295.png 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-1536x589.png 1536w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-2048x785.png 2048w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-720x276.png 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-360x138.png 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-180x69.png 180w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/THE-BEST-DAMN-COOKBOOK-IS-HERE-4-150x58.png 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" class="aligncenter wp-image-23063 size-full"/>
</picture>
</a></p>
</div>
<h2>Simple Pantry Ingredients</h2>
<p>I love to make recipes where I have most of the ingredients already on hand. For this roasted pork tenderloin, we&#8217;ll use a simple rub which includes brown sugar, salt, pepper, <a href="https://amzn.to/42x31vD" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">ground mustard</a>, paprika, onion powder, garlic powder, and a hint of cayenne (optional, be really good).</p>
<p><picture>
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2.jpg.webp 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-241x300.jpg.webp 241w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-822x1024.jpg.webp 822w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-768x957.jpg.webp 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-720x897.jpg.webp 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-360x449.jpg.webp 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-180x224.jpg.webp 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://recipeteacher.com/best-damn-oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin/?tp_image_id=3140" src="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2.jpg" alt="Recipe for oven roasted pork tenderloin" width="1200" height="1495" data-pin-title="Best Damn Oven Roasted Pork Tenderloin" data-pin-description="Make the most delicious oven roasted pork tenderloin with simple ingredients and easy prep. #porktenderloin" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2.jpg 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-241x300.jpg 241w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-822x1024.jpg 822w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-768x957.jpg 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-720x897.jpg 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-360x449.jpg 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin2-180x224.jpg 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3140"/>
</picture>
</p>
<h2>Easy Preparation</h2>
<p>Another reason I love making this recipe is because it&#8217;s so simple to prepare. All you have to do is mix the ingredients together, rub some olive oil on the meat, and then coat it well with the seasoning rub. Place it into a baking dish or pan and into the oven it goes. No need to sear this recipe first, that&#8217;s one less step we needn&#8217;t worry about. Just rub the seasoning on and it&#8217;s ready to go in the oven!</p>
<h2>Roast at 425° (F) for 25-30 minutes</h2>
<p>We want the pork tenderloin to have an internal temperature of 145°(F). An <a href="https://amzn.to/3I8Zyv4" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">instant read thermometer</a> is an essential tool everyone should have on hand. After 25 minutes, check the thickest part of the meat. Once the internal temp is at least 145°(F), you&#8217;re good to remove from the oven. Set the pork tenderloin on a plate and let it sit for at least 5 minutes before slicing and serving.</p>
<p><picture>
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3.jpg.webp 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-225x300.jpg.webp 225w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-768x1024.jpg.webp 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-1152x1536.jpg.webp 1152w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-720x960.jpg.webp 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-360x480.jpg.webp 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-180x240.jpg.webp 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"/>
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://recipeteacher.com/best-damn-oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin/?tp_image_id=3142" src="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3.jpg" alt="Recipe for oven roasted pork tenderloin" width="1200" height="1600" data-pin-title="Best Damn Oven Roasted Pork Tenderloin" data-pin-description="Easy recipe for juicy, tender, oven roasted pork tenderloin. Perfectly seasoned with simple ingredients and roasted in the oven in about 30 minutes." srcset="https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3.jpg 1200w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-225x300.jpg 225w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-720x960.jpg 720w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-360x480.jpg 360w, https://recipeteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/oven-roasted-pork-tenderloin3-180x240.jpg 180w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3142"/>
</picture>
</p>
