		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-194744" data-commentid="194744" data-postid="3104" data-belowelement="article-comment-194744" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Nic" aria-label="Reply to Nic">Reply</a></div>
		
