		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>A few days ago, your Best Damn Oven Roasted Pork Tenderloin appeared in my inbox, and as I was reading the recipe I was convinced I had to make this for dinner that night.<br />
OMG. Am I glad I did &#8212; this pork tenderloin was THE VERY BEST I&#8217;ve ever tasted. And the sandwiches I&#8217;ve made with the leftovers are equally delicious. This will be a permanent addition to my dinner menus. Served with parsley potatoes, steamed broccoli and a glass of very nice Sauvignon Blanc. I went to sleep with a smile on my face!!!</p>
		</div>

